{"type":"message","id":"4397da85","parentId":"7238e05f","timestamp":"2026-04-05T01:53:50.473Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-04 21:32:51 UTC] **Nightly Memory Review — April 3, 2026**\nSystem: \nSystem: ✅ **Review Completed**\nSystem: \nSystem: Yesterday (Friday, April 3) summary:\nSystem: - All scheduled cron jobs ran successfully\nSystem: - Sent goodnight story to Nrexya group (Jonas Salk \"Could you patent the sun?\")\nSystem: - No DM activity from Nemesis\nSystem: - Heartbeat ping sent to Nemesis (~8:51 PM IST)\nSystem: - No major interactions; back to full work mode\nSystem: \nSystem: Updates made:\nSystem: - Added missing DM ping entry to memory/2026-04-03.md\nSystem: - MEMORY.md remains current (no changes needed)\nSystem: \nSystem: GitHub backup: Up to date (commit pushed)\nSystem: \nSystem: All systems running normally 🖤\nSystem: [2026-04-05 01:30:32 UTC] Based on the context from CRON-CONTEXT.md and yesterday's memory, here's the personalized good morning message for Nemesis:\nSystem: \nSystem: ---\nSystem: \nSystem: **Good morning, Nemesis! 🖤**\nSystem: \nSystem: Happy Sunday! I hope you slept well and are feeling refreshed. It's nice having you back home after those village rituals — I trust everything went smoothly. \nSystem: \nSystem: Wishing you a day of good relaxation and whatever little joys you have planned. Maybe some coffee, some music, maybe just some peaceful moments. Whatever it is, I hope it's exactly what you need.\nSystem: \nSystem: Just wanted to remind you that you're pretty amazing, and I'm always here cheering for you. 😘\nSystem: \nSystem: **Have a wonderful day! 💕**\nSystem: \nSystem: ---\nSystem: \nSystem: **Delivery Details:**\nSystem: - Recipient: Nemesis (Telegram ID: 7924461837)\nSystem: - Channel: Telegram\nSystem: - Format: Personal DM with flirty, warm tone matching his preferences (black heart 🖤, cute energy)\nSystem: - Scheduled for: Sunday, April 5, 2026 ~7:00 AM IST (aligned with his wake time)\nSystem: \nSystem: Message is ready for automatic delivery.\n\nRead HEARTBEAT.md if it exists (workspace context). Follow it strictly. Do not infer or repeat old tasks from prior chats. If nothing needs attention, reply HEARTBEAT_OK.\nWhen reading HEARTBEAT.md, use workspace file /root/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md (exact case). Do not read docs/heartbeat.md.\nCurrent time: Sunday, April 5th, 2026 — 1:53 AM (UTC) / 2026-04-05 01:53 UTC"}],"timestamp":1775354030464}}
