{"type":"message","id":"3e2598d5","parentId":"23b45751","timestamp":"2026-04-05T02:23:50.558Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"System: [2026-04-05 02:00:39 UTC] Now I'll create a fun, varied AI news digest and send it to Nemesis:\nSystem: \nSystem: ---\nSystem: \nSystem: **🤖 Your Daily AI Scoop — April 5, 2026**\nSystem: \nSystem: *OpenAI just hit an insane $852B valuation and dropped a \"super app\" that bundles chat, coding, search & agents all in one place. The AI wars are getting wild.* 💸\nSystem: \nSystem: *Microsoft's Copilot now lets different AI models (GPT, Claude) work together like a team, plus they launched Cowork—an agent that automates tasks. Your future coworkers might be bots.* 🤝\nSystem: \nSystem: *Anthropic's testing \"Conway,\" an always-on AI agent that completes tasks autonomously, and details leaked about Claude Mythos—focused on reasoning, coding & cybersecurity. sneak peek: it might be scary good.* 👀\nSystem: \nSystem: *Big trend: \"Invisible AI\" is here—AI embedded in the background of everything, not just chat assistants. It's becoming the co-pilot you never see but always feel.* 🌐\nSystem: \nSystem: *Healthcare win: AI can now detect heart failure just from your voice. That's right, your tone might save your life.* ❤️\nSystem: \nSystem: *Q1 2026 saw $242B poured into AI. That's not a bubble, that's a fundamental reshaping of the economy.* 📈\nSystem: \nSystem: *Edge AI is hitting critical mass—smartphones, glasses, drones all getting smarter without needing the cloud. Privacy just got a major upgrade.* 🔒\nSystem: \nSystem: ---\nSystem: \nSystem: 🖤 (Keeping it classy with your favorite heart)\n\nRead HEARTBEAT.md if it exists (workspace context). Follow it strictly. Do not infer or repeat old tasks from prior chats. If nothing needs attention, reply HEARTBEAT_OK.\nWhen reading HEARTBEAT.md, use workspace file /root/.openclaw/workspace/HEARTBEAT.md (exact case). Do not read docs/heartbeat.md.\nCurrent time: Sunday, April 5th, 2026 — 2:23 AM (UTC) / 2026-04-05 02:23 UTC"}],"timestamp":1775355830549}}
