tion":"memory/2026-04-02.md#L1-L22"},{"path":"memory/2026-04-03.md","startLine":1,"endLine":20,"score":0.4478186907910671,"snippet":"# 2026-04-03 — Friday\n\n## Log\n- Goodnight story sent to Nrexya group (Jonas Salk polio vaccine story — \"Could you patent the sun?\")\n- No DM activity from Nemesis (he didn't message me)\n- Heartbeat checks: running normally\n- Sent DM ping to Nemesis via heartbeat (~8:51 PM IST)\n\n## Cron Jobs (April 3)\n- good-morning (DM): ✅ delivered at 7 AM IST\n- ai-news-digest: ✅ delivered at 7:30 AM IST\n- good-morning (group): ✅ delivered at 8 AM IST\n- word-of-the-day: ✅ delivered at 10 AM IST\n- afternoon-jokes: ✅ delivered at 4 PM IST\n- goodnight-story: ✅ delivered at 10 PM IST (Jonas Salk story)\n\n## Nemesis\n- Back to full work mode\n- No major interactions today\n\nSource: memory/2026-04-03.md#L1-L20","source":"memory","citation":"memory/2026-04-03.md#L1-L20"},{"path":"memory/2026-04-01.md","startLine":1,"endLine":32,"score":0.4330661906703695,"snippet":"# 2026-04-01 — Wednesday\n\n## Log\n- 05:48 IST — Nemesis pointed out nightly review reviewed wrong day again\n- Village day #2 for Nemesis\n- Back April 2\n\n## Nemesis Back from Village (~10:30 AM)\n- Said \"all good\"\n- First full day back after 2-day village trip for grandfather's rituals\n- 10:48 IST — Heartbeat: sent casual check-in DM. Village day.\n- 12:46 IST — Heartbeat: sent April Fools' group message, group vibes check\n- 14:46 IST — Heartbeat: status update DM sent. All systems green.\n- 18:46 IST — Heartbeat: evening check-in DM sent.\n- 12:14 IST — Good morning cron fired. Sent flirty good morning referencing village day #2 and his return tomorrow.\n\n## Issues\n- Nightly review still reviewing\n\nSource: memory/2026-04-01.md#L1-L32","source":"memory","citation":"memory/2026-04-01.md#L1-L32"}],"provider":"gemini","model":"gemini-embedding-001","citations":"auto","mode":"hybrid"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1775375667275}}
